title: NEFF Skate Team Video
description: This is a Neff video of Jordan Hoffart, Adam Dyet, Greg Lutzka, Brandon Biebel and Ryan Decenzo and will be featured in the latest Transworld video "Hallelujah." Check out these Neff skaters as they take it to the streets and parks.
